description:
As you enter Regency Terrace, an immense sense of exclusivity is asserted. This elegant residence is privately nestled in the corner of the cul de sac; providing a privileged life of carefree convenience.

Gracious in its design and generous in its dimensions, the home rests beyond an automatic gated driveway and flaunts a sprawling single-level floorplan where every room benefits from gorgeous garden vistas.

A wide entrance hall greets you at the front door, inviting you to unwind in the refined lounge and dining room.

The open plan kitchen, family and meals area is a social hub with 'wow factor'. It features a pitched roof with clerestory windows, a substantial amount of built-in cabinetry and bench space plus a full suite of white good appliances.

Transitioning outside from here, a fully covered alfresco supplies plenty of room for reclining or entertaining family and friends in private.

Four robed bedrooms are placed for a peaceful night's sleep. The grand master suite boasts two sets of wardrobes and an ensuite with a twin-basin vanity, a large shower and a separate toilet. The remaining rooms share the use of a classy family bathroom and a separate toilet.

Equipped for maximum comfort, the home comes complete with an incredible amount of storage, a large laundry with a drying cupboard, ducted heating, evaporative cooling, a split system air conditioner, ducted vacuum, an alarm, two water tanks with pumps, a sprinkler system and a remote double garage with internal access.

Conveniently positioned, it is within walking distance to bus stops, Landau Drive Reserve and lake, Warranwood Primary School and Melbourne Rudolf Steiner School. It is also situated for easy access to Yarra Valley Grammar, Luther College, McAdam Square, North Ringwood shops, Eastland and Eastlink.

Noel Jones Real Estate has taken every precaution to ensure the information contained herein is true and accurate, however accept no responsibility and disclaim all liability in respect to any errors, omissions, inaccuracies, or misstatements that may occur. Prospective purchasers should make their own enquiries to verify the information contained herein.
